flowchart TD
    U([User question in chat]) --> R{Intent Router<br/>deterministic + LLM-optional}

    R -->|top-N / ranking| A[Analyst Node]
    R -->|trend over time| A
    R -->|anomaly detection| A
    R -->|correlation| A
    R -->|segment comparison| A

    subgraph ING[Ingestion - runs once on load]
        F[/CSV or Excel upload<br/>or Try-sample-data/] --> C[Clean: parse dates,<br/>handle nulls]
        C --> FE[Feature engineering:<br/>shipping_days, order totals,<br/>time + customer features]
        FE --> P[Auto-profile +<br/>self-check assertions]
        P --> DF[(Clean DataFrame<br/>in session_state)]
    end

    DF -.->|live data| A
    A --> EX[Execute analysis<br/>pandas in sandbox]
    EX --> V{Validator Node<br/>independent recompute<br/>matches?}
    V -->|mismatch| A
    V -->|match| NAR[Insight Generator<br/>numbers to narrative]
    NAR --> VIZ[Visualizer<br/>Plotly figure]
    VIZ --> RESP([Answer + chart<br/>rendered in chat])
    RESP -.->|memory: prior question + result| R
